Name: Dynamic Features of VirusShare Executables
Abstract: This dataset contains the dynamic features of 107,888 executables, collected by VirusShare from Nov/2010 to Jul/2014.
RelevantInfo: This dataset contains the dynamic features of 107,888 executables, collected by VirusShare from Nov/2010 to Jul/2014. The features were extracted from the artifacts generated by the executables in the Cukoo Sandbox. Please refer to the paper for more details regarding data collection and feature extraction.
